Package: audiosync-master
Version: 2.0.0
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-adw-1, pulseaudio-utils
Recommends: swh-plugins, pipewire-pulse
Maintainer: Andrei Dumitrescu <andrei@localhost>
Description: Universal Audio Sync for Linux - All Devices Automatic
 Audio Sync Master automatically detects and synchronizes ALL audio
 output devices on your Linux system. Works with PulseAudio and PipeWire.
 .
 Features:
  - Auto-detect ALL analog audio cards and Bluetooth speakers
  - Real-time plug-and-play device monitoring
  - Per-device adjustable delay for perfect sync
  - 10-band parametric EQ with presets
  - Idempotent and safe to restart
  - Modern dark glassmorphism GTK4 UI
  - Works with both PulseAudio and PipeWire
